<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="b27Sep1925"><font color="red">27 September 1925</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Harriet Weaver):  My eyes are getting better &hellip; Having returned from Shaun MacCormack&apos;s concert and having read this, as heretofore, S.O.S. agonising appeal you will, I am sure, agree enthusiastically with somebody somewhere in Shakespearestown that the words of Mercury are harsh after the song of Apollo. But an epilogue there will be. </div>
